  "story": "Every Saturday, three friends run neighbouring stalls at the riverside market, watched over by old Mr. Pemberton, who has kept the market ledger for forty years and still records every sale in sepia ink. This morning Mr. Pemberton misplaced the ledger page, and the stalls all need sorting out before the gates open. Each friend has a different craft. Using the clues, match every friend to their craft.",
